summary: Game of Thrones Margaery Tyrell Breton RaceMenu Chargen Preset
descriptionHtml:
My version of the Game of Thrones character Margaery Tyrell (played by Natalie Dorner). This is a BRETON Female character preset that works with RaceMenu only.


[b]Install with NMM[/b]

To use it either start a new game or hit ` (above the tab key) and then type "showracemenu" (without the " ), hit enter and then ` key again. You can find her face on the ALL or BODY tab. Just move the top slider, called "Preset Slot", to 45 and hit F9 key. Note that this is just a Face Preset. You have to adjust the body on your own.

[b]*IMPORTANT!*[/b] Do NOT change the race of an existing character. It creates bugs in racial bonuses. If your character is not already a Breton you should probably start a new game if you want this face.


[b]These mods are required for the presets to work:[/b]
- SKSE --- http://skse.silverlock.org/
- Racemenu --- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?


[b]These following mods are optional[/b] but needed to make her look exactly like in the screenshot. She will still look more or less similar if you don't have/want some of these. Download and install in this order, click yes to overwrite:
- Dimonized UNP Female body (Adult Content) --- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?
- SG Female Texures Renewal UNP (Adult Content) --- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?
- The Eyes OF Beauty PLAYER --- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
- Brows Normal --- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?
- ApachiiSkyHair_v_1_5_Full --- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?

If you don't like the glossiness of ApachiiskyHair you can also download this mod that will make those hairstyles blend in better with vanilla Skyrim hair:
- ApachiiSKyHair a NATURAL retexture (it has several different v_1_5_Full versions, pick one you like) --- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35092/?

Hair flower and dress. Note that these are equippable items you have to find in the game after you download those mods:
- Menno Hairflowers --- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/38728/?
- Witcher 2 Ehlhart Dress --- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36738/?

Other things:
Even though SG Female Texture Renewal has Enhanced Character Edit listed as required, I do not use it. No idea if installing it alters how Racemenu presets looks or not.
author: Izuela
